 brązowe liście i wygląda na uschnięty? Sprawdź, jak uratować krzew po zimie. Poznaj triki na podlewanie, cięcie i nawożenie różaneczników.","porady ogrodnicze, ogród, marzec, rododendrony",{"value":1601},{"filename":88,"name":88,"tags":88,"thumbnail":88,"type":88,"url":88},"https://magazynona.pl/blog/ona-w-ogrodzie/twoj-rododendron-wyglada-po-zimie-jak-uschniety-ten-prosty-trik-przywroci-mu-zycie/6lkcp1BMiXGBsxTo2P1n","magazynona.pl","6lkcp1BMiXGBsxTo2P1n","2026-03-11 14:15:00","https://jarocinska.pl/kobieta-i-dziecko/twoj-rododendron-wyglada-po-zimie-jak-uschniety-ten-prosty-trik-przywroci-mu-zycie/Q7bCSEt3UntdFKoHZPCO","twoj-rododendron-wyglada-po-zimie-jak-uschniety-ten-prosty-trik-przywroci-mu-zycie","Twój rododendron wygląda po zimie jak uschnięty?",[1610,1611,1612,1613],"ogród","porady ogrodnicze","rododendrony","marzec",[1615,1617,1619,1620],{"tag":1610,"slug":1616},"ogrod",{"tag":1611,"slug":1618},"porady-ogrodnicze",{"tag":1612,"slug":1612},{"tag":1613,"slug":1613},"Twój rododendron wygląda po zimie jak uschnięty? Ten prosty trik przywróci mu życie","2026-03-11 14:15:22",["Reactive",1624],{"ads":29,"aid":1625,"alternative_gallery_style":29,"attachments":1626,"author":1413,"author_info":44,"category":1634,"comments":29,"comments_auth":29,"content":91,"created_by":1415,"created_by_name":91,"custom_html":88,"featured":44,"gallery_ads":1635,"gallery_picked":1636,"id":1687,"is_advertisement":44,"is_photostory":44,"is_pool":13,"multiportal":88,"view_type":88,"is_redirect":44,"keywords":1688,"lead":1702,"locked":13,"meta":1703,"parent_domain":88,"parent_id":88,"photostory_added":29,"pool_picked":1709,"pool_under_photostory":28,"premium":44,"published":13,"published_at":1734,"quiz_picked":88,"recommended":44,"redirect_url":88,"self_url":1735,"show_quiz_cover":28,"slug":1736,"sponsored":28,"short_title":1737,"tags":1738,"tagsRaw":1741,"title":1704,"type":1176,"uid":1687,"updated_at":1745},73469,[1627],{"id":1628,"name":1629,"url":1630,"thumbnail":1630,"created_at":